OL,3,CFive officers injured after police
OL,4,Cboat on Thames strikes Westminster
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FFive officers have been injured after
OL,8,Fa police boat struck Westminster
OL,9,FBridge on the River Thames in central
OL,10,FLondon, the Met Police said.
OL,12,FAt around 3.40pm on Friday afternoon,
OL,13,Fa boat from the Met's Marine Policing
OL,14,FUnit collided with Westminster Bridge.
OL,16,FA number of officers entered the water
OL,17,Fbut were later recovered and were seen
OL,18,Fbeing treated by paramedics on a rigid
OL,19,Fblack inflatable boat moored alongside
OL,20,Fthe river.
