OL,3,CFive officers injured after police
OL,4,Cboat on Thames strikes Westminster
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FOfficers have cordoned off a section
OL,8,Fof the bridge overlooking the Houses
OL,9,Fof Parliament.
OL,11,FA large number of police officers,
OL,12,Ffire crews and ambulances are at the
OL,13,Fscene, with traffic across the bridge
OL,14,Fbrought to a standstill.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Met said: "At
OL,17,Faround 3.45pm on Friday July 24 a boat
OL,18,Ffrom the Met's Marine Policing Unit
OL,19,Fstruck Westminster Bridge.
