OL,3,CFive officers injured after police
OL,4,Cboat on Thames strikes Westminster
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,F"A number of officers entered the
OL,8,Fwater but were recovered.
OL,10,F"Additional officers responded
OL,11,Falongside the London Ambulance Service
OL,12,Fand London Fire Brigade.
OL,14,F"We understand five officers were
OL,15,Finjured and are receiving treatment.
OL,16,FWe await an update on the extent of
OL,17,Ftheir injuries.
OL,19,F"At this stage, we don't believe any
OL,20,Fmembers of the public were involved or
OL,21,Finjured.
