OL,3,CFive officers injured after police
OL,4,Cboat on Thames strikes Westminster
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,F"The circumstances of the incident
OL,8,Fwill be thoroughly reviewed, but at
OL,9,Fthis stage our priority is the
OL,10,Fwellbeing of the officers involved."
