OL,3,CFive officers injured after police
OL,4,Cboat on Thames strikes Westminster
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,F"We are supporting the response and
OL,8,Fproviding assistance where needed,
OL,9,Fworking closely with the Metropolitan
OL,10,FPolice, HM Coastguard and partner
OL,11,Fagencies to manage the situation."
OL,13,FA police helicopter and an air
OL,14,Fambulance were circling above.
OL,16,FEntrances three and four to
OL,17,FWestminster Underground station have
OL,18,Fbeen shut, Transport for London has
OL,19,Fconfirmed.
